Dylan Miller is a senior at Juniata College studying English and philosophy . 
  He decided to live in a hut for a research project on simple living . 
  He built the structure out of fallen trees, leaves and a tarp . 
  There is no plumbing or electricity in the hut and he has to study by lantern . 
  He hopes to better understand writers Henry David Thoreau and Ralph Waldo Emerson . 
 